

- FAQ -

Q: What is TakeScreenshot's privacy policy?
A: We do not collect any personal data at all.


Q: How can I take a screenshot?
A: Click or tap on the AppIcon and select Take Screenshot.


Q: Why doesn't the screen capture work?
A: Please ensure that you allowed the screen recording in the security settings on your Mac.

Q: How can i turn off the application?
A: Click or tap on the AppIcon and select Quit.

Q: If I have multiple screens, which one does it take a picture of?
A: At the moment from your main screen.


